## Why This Is Asked
Tests ability to design cross-account access with least privilege, IAM trust policies, KMS, and auditing; understands CloudTrail, bucket policies.

## Key Concepts
- Cross-account IAM roles and trust policies
- S3 bucket policies and access controls
- KMS key policies and encryption scope
- CloudTrail validation and rotation awareness

## Code Example
```json
{
  \"Version\": \"2012-10-17\",
  \"Statement\": [
    {
      \"Effect\": \"Allow\",
      \"Principal\": {\"AWS\": \"arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_A:role/ServiceRoleA\"},
      \"Action\": \"sts:AssumeRole\"
    }
  ]
}
```

```json
{
  \"Version\": \"2012-10-17\",
  \"Statement\": [
    {
      \"Effect\": \"Allow\",
      \"Principal\": {\"AWS\": \"arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_A:role/ServiceRoleA\"},
      \"Action\": \"s3:GetObject\",
      \"Resource\": \"arn:aws:s3:::bucket-b/data/*\"
    },
    {
      \"Effect\": \"Allow\",
      \"Principal\": {\"AWS\": \"arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_A:role/ServiceRoleA\"},
      \"Action\": \"s3:ListBucket\",
      \"Resource\": \"arn:aws:s3:::bucket-b\"
    }
  ]
}
```

```json
{
  \"Version\": \"2012-10-17\",
  \"Statement\": [
    {
      \"Effect\": \"Allow\",
      \"Principal\": {\"AWS\": \"arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_B:role/DataReadRole\"},
      \"Action\": [\"kms:Decrypt\",\"kms:Encrypt\",\"kms:ReEncrypt*\",\"kms:GenerateDataKey*\"],
      \"Resource\": \"arn:aws:kms:REGION:ACCOUNT_B:key/KEYID\"
    }
  ]
}
```

## Follow-up Questions
- How would you handle key rotation frequency and auditing across accounts?
- How would you test access isolation and ensure no other principals can assume the role?

## Why This Is Asked
Tests cross-account trust, least privilege S3/KMS usage, no Internet constraint, and auditability.

## Key Concepts
- Cross-account role trust
- S3 bucket policy with path-level scoping
- KMS policy for decrypt/encrypt
- No Internet access
- Immutable auditing

## Code Example
```javascript
// Trust policy excerpt for DataAccessRole
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": {"AWS": "arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_A:role/ProcessorRole"},
      "Action": "sts:AssumeRole"
    }
  ]
}
```
```javascript
// Bucket policy excerpt (data-inbound)
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": {"AWS": "arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_B:role/DataAccessRole"},
      "Action": ["s3:GetObject", "s3:ListBucket"],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::data-inbound",
        "arn:aws:s3:::data-inbound/data-inbound/*"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": {"AWS": "arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_B:role/DataAccessRole"},
      "Action": "s3:PutObject",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::data-out/*"
    }
  ]
}
```
```javascript
// KMS key policy snippet (CMK in Security account)
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Principal": {"AWS": "arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_B:role/DataAccessRole"},
      "Action": ["kms:Decrypt","kms:GenerateDataKey*","kms:Encrypt"],
      "Resource": "*"
    }
  ]
}
```

## Follow-up Questions
- How would you test for privilege creep?
- How would you rotate the CMK without downtime?

## Why This Is Asked
Evaluates expertise in architecting secure, scalable data science environments with strict least-privilege controls across multi-account data lakes, requiring mastery of ABAC, Lake Formation, KMS, and private networking.

## Key Concepts
- Attribute-based access control (ABAC) with IAM policy tags
- Lake Formation fine-grained permissions
- SageMaker notebook cross-account trust relationships
- Private connectivity through VPC endpoints
- Centralized CMK with rotation policies
- Immutable audit logging via CloudTrail
- Automated drift and privilege-creep detection

## Code Example
```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": ["s3:GetObject"],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::data-lake/${aws:PrincipalTag/project}/*",
      "Condition": {
        "StringEquals": {
          "s3:ExistingObjectTag/dataset": "${aws:PrincipalTag/dataset}"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```
